blueprint.label: Vanilla Depot Hub
blueprint.description:
This will support up to 8 trains waiting for schedules and provide fuel to any BT trains that need it.

This blueprint is set for nuclear fuel! Earlier in the game, you'll need to change it in two places: (a) the station name and (b) the configuration combinator. Change the request to one of:

-800 rocket fuel, or
-2500 solid fuel, or
-2500 coal

Note the NEGATIVE numbers.

entities.name: arithmetic-combinator
entities.player_description:
Calculate the average number of items per chest.
Using only the first car because a short-train could leave it empty while later cars make the station think it has capacity.
